txt.en: 'Who might you be? I do not believe I have seen you in the hen-house before. Well, no matter.\n\n'Are those earthworms you have for me? I simply will not eat anything but earthworms these days. I have not taken well to the new feed in the yard.'
Scratch at the ground to reveal earthworms in Farmer Sandson's field.
Billina is in the yard at Sandson's Farm west of Sandson's Fields.\n\nNow that you have collected some earthworms, you should speak with Billina.
